{"text_id":105911,"tokens":["How"," to"," Play"," Hand","bells","\n","Playing"," hand","bells"," is"," an"," exciting"," way"," to"," show"," off"," your"," musical"," skills",","," and"," it"," is"," a"," great"," way"," to"," become"," part"," of"," a"," group","."," Whether"," you"," find"," yourself"," in"," a"," chorus"," of"," bells"," or"," seren","ading"," solo",","," joining"," a"," hand","bell"," choir"," will"," add"," a"," sense"," of"," camaraderie"," and"," teamwork"," to"," your"," musical"," repertoire","."," The"," following"," steps"," will"," help"," you"," master"," the"," basics"," of"," playing"," hand","bells",".","\n\n","Find"," a"," hand","bell"," choir"," in"," your"," area","."," Joining"," a"," hand","bell"," choir"," is"," a"," great"," way"," to"," start"," learning"," the"," ropes","."," Many"," churches"," and"," community"," organizations"," have"," hand","bell"," choirs"," that"," are"," always"," looking"," for"," new"," talent","."," You"," can"," even"," find"," them"," online",".","\n\n","Know"," some"," basic"," music"," fundamentals",","," or"," be"," prepared"," to"," learn"," them"," fairly"," quickly","."," Understanding"," key"," signatures",","," tempo"," markings",","," and"," time"," signatures"," will"," be"," helpful"," when"," you"," are"," beginning"," to"," learn"," hand","bells",".","\n\n","Understand"," the"," basic"," idea"," of"," a"," hand","bell"," choir","."," A"," hand","bell"," choir"," is"," a"," group"," of"," people"," that"," use"," hand","bells"," to"," play"," musical"," pieces",","," similar"," to"," a"," choral"," group"," that"," sings",".","\n\n","Familiar","ize"," yourself"," with"," the"," anatomy"," of"," a"," hand","bell","."," A"," hand","bell"," consists"," of"," a"," bell",","," a"," handle",","," and"," a"," cla","pper","."," A"," more"," sensitive"," model"," of"," hand","bells"," have"," a"," padded"," handle"," to"," make"," them"," easier"," to"," play",".","\n\n","Begin"," by"," putting"," on"," gloves"," (","worn"," by"," most"," choirs"," to"," avoid"," sm","udging"," or"," tarn","ishing"," the"," hand","bells",")"," and"," picking"," up"," two"," bells"," and"," holding"," them"," in"," front"," of"," your"," chest",","," either"," angling"," towards"," you"," or"," facing"," straight"," up",","," depending"," on"," the"," way"," your"," choir"," has"," chosen"," to"," stand"," with"," the"," bells"," up",".","\n\n","To"," ring"," one"," bell",","," move"," it"," forward"," by"," extending"," it"," away"," from"," your"," body"," in"," a"," circular"," motion",","," with"," the"," handle"," moving"," slightly"," ahead"," of"," the"," bell","."," This"," motion"," is"," known"," as"," an"," \"","arc",".\""," The"," arc"," should"," begin"," at"," your"," chest"," and"," rise"," up",","," then"," swoop"," down"," to"," create"," a"," circular"," motion",".","\n\n","Damp"," the"," bell"," by"," touching"," it"," lightly"," to"," your"," chest"," when"," you"," complete"," the"," circle","."," This"," will"," prevent"," the"," bell"," from"," continually"," ringing",".","\n\n","Repeat"," until"," you"," are"," comfortable"," with"," this"," motion",","," and"," then"," try"," with"," the"," other"," bell"," in"," your"," other"," hand","."," You"," will"," need"," to"," become"," comfortable"," with"," both"," hands"," and"," alternating"," them"," in"," order"," to"," keep"," playing",".","\n\n","Understand"," that"," the"," length"," of"," time"," you"," spend"," ringing"," (","and"," thus",","," the"," size"," of"," your"," circle",")"," varies"," according"," to"," the"," length"," of"," the"," note"," you"," are"," playing","."," Short"," notes",","," such"," as"," sta","cc","atos",","," will"," need"," a"," short",","," fast"," circle","."," Long"," notes",","," such"," as"," leg","atos",","," will"," need"," a"," longer",","," larger"," circle",".","\n\n","Understand"," your"," role"," as"," a"," member"," of"," a"," hand","bell"," choir","."," Hand","bell"," choirs"," are"," usually"," divided"," into"," two"," parts",","," the"," ten","ors"," and"," the"," tre","bles","."," The"," ten","ors"," ring"," the"," bells"," that"," have"," a"," lower"," pitch",","," while"," the"," tre","bles"," play"," the"," bells"," with"," a"," higher"," pitch",".","\n\n","Mark"," your"," music",","," if"," you"," find"," it"," helpful"," at"," first","."," Feel"," free"," to"," make"," notes",","," put"," in"," pauses",","," and"," practice"," difficult"," passages",".","\n\n","Keep"," the"," beat","."," Keeping"," a"," steady"," rhythm"," while"," playing"," hand","bells"," is"," extremely"," important",","," as"," it"," will"," help"," you"," stay"," in"," the"," same"," tempo"," with"," the"," rest"," of"," the"," choir",".","\n\n","Have"," fun","."," While"," playing"," in"," a"," hand","bell"," choir"," can"," be"," challenging",","," it"," can"," also"," be"," an"," extremely"," rewarding"," experience","."," Don","\u2019","t"," be"," afraid"," to"," smile"," and"," enjoy"," yourself"," as"," you"," play",".","\n\n","Once"," you"," have"," mastered"," basic"," hand","bell"," playing"," fundamentals",","," move"," on"," to"," more"," advanced"," techniques","."," Try"," playing"," with"," mal","lets",","," plu","cking"," the"," bells",","," and"," playing"," bells"," four","-"," and"," six","-","in","-","hand","."," If"," you","\u2019","re"," feeling"," adventurous",","," you"," may"," even"," venture"," into"," the"," art"," of"," solo"," hand","bells","."," By"," improving"," and"," perfecting"," your"," technique",","," you"," may"," even"," get"," an"," opportunity"," to"," perform"," solo"," or"," with"," a"," group"," of"," hand","bell"," enthusiasts","."],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"davinci","label":1}